name: Please Stand By -I Got Something To Say 095
description: Please Stand By utilizes the iconic SMPTE color bars template and changes the palette to bring into question viewers perceptions surrounding "standards of color." An offshoot of my original series, I Got Something To Say, adds an additional more literal message. Please Stand By, For The Next 500K Mints. Celebrating the first 500K items minted on Hicetnunc. Here's to a long life with at least another 500K mints!
